snippet.title: Star Command - Release Trailer (OFFICIAL)
snippet.description:
Build and command your own starship! 

Arriving May 2nd on iPad, iPhone and iPod Touch.

Android coming very soon.

Star Command let's you build your own ship, hire your crew, explore the universe and battle alien civilizations across the galaxy.

http://www.starcommandgame.com
http://www.facebook.com/starcommandgame
http://twitter.com/StarCommandGame

Music: Marius Masalar
http://mathazzar.com/
https://twitter.com/Mathazzar
